<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Landing Page Section</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
        }
        a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        a:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>Welcome to Our Landing Page</h1>
    <p>This is a simple landing page section showcasing some basic HTML and CSS.</p>
    <p>You can customize this section to fit your specific needs, add more content, and style it further.</p>
    <a href="#">Learn More</a>
</div>
</body>
</html>